{"tid":1291711,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國重申華為繼續列入貿易黑名單","createTime":"2019-07-07T04:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T00:28:37.000Z","uid":66271,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5b1da0d6a571a9bb2dd47ec831ebf32e82d2f802","tid":1291711,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:13:56.000Z","msg":"　<br />\n美國官員透露，美中高層已就貿易問題對話，相信很快會舉行會談，但重申華為會繼續列入貿易黑名單，不能參與美國的5G建設。<br />\n　　<br />\n南非總統拉馬福薩在當地一個數碼經濟論壇演說，指美國無法想像4G以後的世界，因而封殺技術已超越自己的華為。當地的電訊網絡供應商均希望發展5G網絡，認為只有華為才能協助他們建設。但現時華為被美國制裁，亦連累到南非的電訊發展，因此南非要與華為同一陣線。<br />\n　　"},{"pid":"fe100ce2cd6a1501fbc2364b7f14c152e32605e7","tid":1291711,"uid":60434,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:14:43.000Z","msg":"華為打風都打唔甩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea48489a7eb6d59f6ba3188f6ab120647e0f2e5","tid":1291711,"uid":997,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:26:27.000Z","msg":"Trump : 國會唔比"},{"pid":"cacf9d06d0f458e20480ba238175ff81e756b0f8","tid":1291711,"uid":246764,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:01:57.000Z","msg":"侵侵: 疏V<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd820f5e6c6f5d3eb082e04c5532524e5fa023a5","tid":1291711,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:03:16.000Z","msg":"咁會唔會繼續供貨先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0073ff750353d44209c551c390ce2ba56e551a","tid":1291711,"uid":264908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"繼續撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36eaff785217b7c44a4c39b7e1dde5b5d2e8312","tid":1291711,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"唔理你係和理非定勇武都入一入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1291764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht